{
  "stem": "6258.6",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "After the war.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Well, we knew from the very beginning of the war that there is no-- that our only hope it was--",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I still did not know.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I know this but well because of this.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "That they run away.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We were taken back to Plaszow.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I might have them somewhere.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "[NON-ENGLISH] was one.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I know that they survived.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In nachrichtengeratenlager, I was alone.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They were in Plaszow.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And at this time, my father already was sent to Auschwitz and executed.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And gassed.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But I did not know it.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I just knew that he was sent on about between 13 or 15th of May, that he was sent to, as they said, matches factory in Birkenau.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Nobody knew about Birkenau.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "People knew about Auschwitz, that there is  a camp.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But we did not know what was going on.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But we did not know about Birkenau.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And in Birkenau were the gas chambers.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "So my father was not anymore there.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "But when  I came back to Plaszow, I was with my mother, and my brother was there.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It was-- well, this was too a small of camp to be, you know, so-- so-- but they were-- there was-- the head of this camp was such a small, short guy.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "His  name was Krak, K-R-A-K.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And he was-- he showed up one day into our barrack in the evening.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I was in my, you know, [INAUDIBLE] in my bed, doing something.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And the girls were all sitting around the table and eating the soup.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And when he came-- so attention.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Everybody should stay attention.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So I stayed at attention too.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But about three seconds later then everybody else, till I get out of this-- of this thing.",
      "word_count": 17
    }
  ],
